{"uid": "service-dependencies", "title": "3 - Service Dependencies & Traces", "tags": ["workshop", "tracing", "bug"], "timezone": "browser", "schemaVersion": 16, "version": 0, "refresh": "5s", "panels": [{"id": 10, "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}, "type": "text", "title": "", "options": {"mode": "html", "content": "<div style='font-family:Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding:12px 16px;color:#d8d9da;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px'><div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:0 0 8px 0'>How to Trigger</p><div style='background:#1a1b1f;border:1px solid #2c3235;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 16px;font-family:monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:#73bf69'>$ oha -z 60s -c 5 http://localhost/api/orders/20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001</div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:16px 0 4px 0'>Location</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0;font-family:monospace'>service-b/src/handlers.rs \u2014 get_order() ~line 217</p></div><div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:0 0 8px 0'>What's Happening</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0 0 10px 0'>Each order contains 50 line items with different products. Instead of fetching all products in one batch, Service B calls Service C once per product \u2014 50 sequential HTTP requests per order. This is the classic N+1 query pattern.</p><p style='font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;color:#8e8e8e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 4px 0'>How to identify</p><ul style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0 0 10px 0;padding-left:16px'><li>B\u2192C call rate is ~50\u00d7 the inbound rate to Service B</li><li>In Tempo: one order trace shows 50 sequential child spans to Service C</li><li>Service C error rate spikes as its connection pool saturates</li></ul><p style='font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;color:#8e8e8e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 4px 0'>The Fix</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0'>Add <code style='background:#1a1b1f;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px'>POST /api/products/batch</code> to Service C and replace the per-item loop in Service B with a single batched call.</p></div></div>"}}, {"id": 1, "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10}, "type": "nodeGraph", "title": "Service Dependency Map", "datasource": {"uid": "tempo", "type": "tempo"}, "targets": [{"queryType": "serviceMap", "refId": "A"}]}, {"id": 2, "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 20}, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Service B \u2192 Service C Call Rate", "description": "Should see 50x multiplier due to N+1 bug", "targets": [{"expr": "rate(traces_service_graph_request_total{client=\"service-b-orders\",server=\"service-c-products\"}[1m])", "legendFormat": "B \u2192 C requests/sec", "refId": "A"}, {"expr": "sum by (service) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-b-orders\"}[1m]))", "legendFormat": "B inbound requests/sec", "refId": "B"}], "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10}, "unit": "reqps"}}}, {"id": 3, "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 20}, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Service C - Request Rate & Errors", "description": "Pool exhaustion shows as error rate spike", "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-c-products\"}[1m]))", "legendFormat": "Total requests", "refId": "A"}, {"expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-c-products\",status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[1m]))", "legendFormat": "Errors", "refId": "B"}], "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10}, "unit": "reqps"}, "overrides": [{"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Errors"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red"}}]}]}}, {"id": 5, "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 29}, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Service B - Response Latency (p50 / p99)", "description": "User-visible consequence of N+1: each order waits for 50 sequential upstream calls, so p99 is orders of magnitude higher than a healthy service.", "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-b-orders\"}[1m])))", "legendFormat": "p50", "refId": "A"}, {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-b-orders\"}[1m])))", "legendFormat": "p99", "refId": "B"}], "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"custom": {"drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2}, "unit": "ms"}, "overrides": [{"matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "p99"}, "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red"}}]}]}}, {"id": 20, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 37}, "type": "text", "title": "", "options": {"mode": "html", "content": "<div style='font-family:Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding:8px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:flex-end;height:100%'><a href='/d/database-connections' style='display:inline-block;padding:8px 24px;background:#ff9830;color:#111;border-radius:6px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;text-decoration:none'>\u2192 Next: 4 - Database Connection Pools</a></div>"}}], "time": {"from": "now-2m", "to": "now"}}